descriptionHtml:
[center][/center][center][size=5][b]Easy Teleport Magic[/b][/size][/center][center]
This mods is a simple mod for people teleport to any big point.
Also you can use the big map to transfer, but sometimes and someplace also not easy to go.This is a magic like MTR to teleport to different big point of skyrim.

  [img]https://staticdelivery.nexusmods.com/mods/110/images/91300/91300-1526140495-1451952181.jpeg[/img]﻿

V1.0 Location on is already be in below list, and this mod will keepling update it.[/center][list]
